            <b>Online Survey on Needs of the Water Sector Concerning Compet=
ence=20
            Modelling<br>
            </b>The project WACOM transfers the European Qualification Fram=
ework=20
            (EQF) and the German Reference Model for the Competence Modelli=
ng=20
            PAS 1093 in the water sector and its Vocational Education and T=
raining=20
            (VET) system throughout whole Europe. The major result of the W=
ACOM=20
            project is the creation of a competence model in the sewage tre=
atment=20
            plants (<a href=3D"http://www.wacom-project.eu/">http://www.wac=
om-project.eu</a>).<br>
            <br>
            In this context, an online survey has been launched. It aims to=
 identify=20
            the current level of awareness and knowledge of participants up=
on=20
            the needs in the water sector and competences modelling.<br>
            <br>
            Topics of this survey include the following issues:<br>
            <br>
            * Current Awareness of Competence Standards<br>
            <br>
            * Perceived Need of the implementation of Competences Model in =
the=20
            Water Sector<br>
            <br>
            * Vocational Education and Training in Water Sector<br>
            <br>
            The results of the Online Survey will contribute to the identif=
ication=20
            of the needs in the water sector and will be integrated into th=
e competence=20
            model that will be created in the WACOM project.<br>
            <br>
            Your opinion is of great value to us. Therefore we would like t=
o ask=20
            you for your participation in our survey. Please, follow the li=
nk:=20
            <br>
            <br>
            See: <a href=3D"http://survey.agroknow.gr/index.php?sid=3D38344=
&amp;newtest=3DY&amp;lang=3Den">http://survey.agroknow.gr/index.php?sid=3D3=
8344&amp;newtest=3DY&amp;lang=3Den</a><br>
            <br>
            The questionnaire can be accessed in 5 languages (English, Germ=
an,=20
            Greek, Hungarian and Romanian) and will take about 15 minutes t=
o complete.=20
            To get familiarized with the questions of the survey, you can b=
rowse=20
            through them using the &quot;Back&quot; and &quot;Next&quot; bu=
tton.=20
            But please do not proceed after the questions related to your p=
ersonal=20
            info, because then the questionnaire will be considered complet=
